definitions.definition: Any small monkey , now specifically a Central and South American monkey of the genera Callithrix , Mico , Cebuella , and Callibella , with claws instead of nails, and a rather primitive layout.

main_definition: Any small monkey , now specifically a Central and South American monkey of the genera Callithrix , Mico , Cebuella , and Callibella , with claws instead of nails, and a rather primitive layout. [from 14th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( obsolete ) A hideous figure ; a grotesque . [15th–19th c.]
( derogatory , now rare ) An unappealing or foolish man . [from 16th c.]
